{res}{txt}
{com}. twoway (line mean_cap year, yaxis(1)) (line mean_no_cap year, yaxis(2)), legend(order(1 "ln_cas_cap", 2 "ln_cas_no_cap"))
{err}, not an integer, option order() ignored
